    <!--section 2 -->

    <!--section video -->
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 mt-16">
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden pb-[40%]">
            <iframe
                class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full"
                src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/rKE-aUoKWhE?si=Hix0Wt-am77ezPpB"
                title="YouTube video player"
                frameborder="0"
                allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
                referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin"
                allowfullscreen
            >
            </iframe>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- -->
    <div class="container mx-auto p-6">
        <!-- Main Container -->
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row">
            <!-- Text Section -->
            <div class="p-6 md:w-2/3">
                <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-maroon font-bold">
                    Pakistan’s Water Crisis
                </h2>
                <p
                    class="mt-2 text-grey text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-justify"
                >
                    Despite <a
                        href="#"
                        class="font-bold text-maroon hover:text-customBeige"
                        >recent floods</a
                    >, water is still scarce in parts of Pakistan. Only 40% of
                    Pakistani people have reliable access to safe drinking
                    water. With a growing population, high levels of poverty,
                    and plagued by natural disasters, Pakistan is facing a water
                    crisis.
                </p>
                <p
                    class="mt-2 text-grey text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-justify"
                >
                    Children and the elderly are the most at risk from
                    water-borne illness and poor sanitation. Almost half of
                    deaths in the country are related to the contaminated water
                    supply. At Al-Wahab Foundation, our priority is to ensure
                    that underprivileged communities have access to clean
                    drinking water to protect and save their lives. From
                    sustainable and <span class="font-bold"
                        >well-maintained water pumps to water wells</span
                    >, your donation can help us achieve our goal. Donate water
                    pump in Pakistan and help those in need.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Image Section -->
            <div class="md:w-1/3 flex-shrink-0">
                <img
                    src="/assets/images/2022/06/IMG_0123-847x1024.jpg"
                    alt="Water Crisis Image"
                    class="w-96 h-96 object-cover"
                />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container mx-auto p-6">
        <!-- Main Container -->
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row">
            <!-- Image Section -->
            <div class="md:w-1/3 flex-shrink-0">
                <img
                    src="/assets/images/2022/06/IMG_18441a.jpg"
                    alt="Water Crisis Image"
                    class="w-96 h-96 object-cover"
                />
            </div>
            <!-- Text Section -->
            <div class="p-6 md:w-2/3">
                <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-maroon font-bold">
                    Water Crisis in Uganda
                </h2>
                <p
                    class="mt-2 text-grey text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-justify"
                >
                    Africa faces a severe water crisis, with a significant
                    portion of its population lacking access to clean and safe
                    water sources. The scarcity of clean water poses a
                    significant threat to public health and exacerbates the
                    vulnerability of communities, particularly women and
                    children, to waterborne diseases. In response to this
                    situation specifically <a
                        href="#"
                        class="font-bold text-maroon hover:text-customBeige"
                        >poverty in Uganda,</a
                    >, Al-Wahab Foundation’s water project aims at providing
                    sustainable water solutions to those in need.
                </p>
                <p
                    class="mt-2 text-grey text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-justify"
                >
                    By donating to <span class="font-bold">
                        Al-Wahab Foundation’s water project
                    </span>for Uganda, you can directly contribute to
                    alleviating the water crisis and improving the lives of
                    countless individuals. Your support will enable the
                    implementation of installing water wells and pumps. Donate
                    water well or hand pump today and be a part of this
                    life-changing initiative.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!--section 3 -->

    <RestoringLives ReStroingLives={Restoring} />
    <!--section 5  -->
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="row">
            <p
                class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-maroon font-bold mt-10 sm:mt-20"
            >
                What is Al-Wahab Foundation has achieved so far?
            </p>
            <p
                class="mt-5 sm:mt-7 text-grey text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-justify"
            >
                At Al-Wahab Foundation we believe in <a
                    href="#"
                    class="text-maroon hover:text-customBeige"
                    >serving humanity</a
                > with compassion and generosity, to relieve the hardships of those
                who are disadvantaged or suffering. Our mission is to expand our
                network to serve more people, especially in the vulnerable areas
                of Pakistan where water remains unsafe or unavailable due to lack
                of infrastructure. With your help, we can reach communities in remote
                areas and ensure that your donations support those in the greatest
                need. <span class="font-bold">Donate water well</span> or <span
                    class="font-bold">water pump</span
                > now to help people access water that is clean and safe.
            </p>
            <p
                class="mt-5 sm:mt-7 text-grey text-base sm:text-lg font-bold text-justify"
            >
                Here is an overview of what we have achieved so far:
            </p>
            <p
                class="mt-2 text-maroon sm:text-lg font-bold text-2xl text-justify"
            >
                Water Pump Charity & Installation
            </p>
            <p
                class="mt-2 text-grey text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-justify"
            >
                With your <a
                    href="#"
                    class="text-maroon hover:text-customBeige font-bold"
                    >Sadaqah</a
                > and <a
                    href="#"
                    class="text-maroon hover:text-customBeige font-bold"
                    >Zakat donation</a
                >, we are on the ground working to transform lives for those who
                need it the most. For more than 10 years, <span
                    class="font-bold">Al-Wahab Foundation</span
                > has been working in rural areas across Pakistan, installing freshwater
                sources to provide clean water. To date, we have installed 4,772
                hand pumps facilitating 121,800 beneficiaries and we aim to expand
                it for a better reach out with your continued support to water pump
                project.
            </p>
            <p
                class="mt-5 text-maroon sm:text-lg font-bold text-2xl text-justify"
            >
                Water Well Donation & Installationn
            </p>
            <p
                class="mt-2 text-grey text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-justify"
            >
                Your contribution towards our <span class="font-bold"
                    >Water for Life project</span
                > is the driving force behind our transformative work, reaching those
                who need it most. Al-Wahab Foundation has been actively operating
                in rural areas across Pakistan, ensuring access to clean water by
                supporting water well project. We have accomplished installing 443
                water wells providing fresh water sources to 110,750 beneficiaries.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!--section 4 -->
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="row">
            <p class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-maroon font-bold mt-6">
                Donate Water Well, Water Pump, and Change Lives for Good
            </p>
            <p
                class="mt-2 text-grey text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-justify"
            >
                Your support can turn the tide for countless communities
                struggling without clean water. Give the gift of life, hope, and
                transformation by generously <span class="font-bold"
                    >donating a water well</span
                > or water pump charity to <span class="font-bold"
                    >Al-Wahab Foundation’s Water for Life Project.</span
                > Together, we can create a lasting and profound change, providing
                a brighter, healthier future for the most vulnerable communities.
            </p>
            <p class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-maroon font-bold mt-6">
                Be The Change
            </p>
            <p
                class="mt-2 text-grey text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-justify"
            >
                The change begins with you, and your decision to donate a water
                well or water pump can be a catalyst for change that resonates
                across generations. Embrace the opportunity to be the
                change-maker in the lives of those who are yearning for the gift
                of clean water with <a
                    href="#"
                    class="text-maroon hover:text-customBeige font-bold"
                    >Al-Wahab Foundation.</a
                >
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-center mt-10 sm:mt-12">
            <a
                href="#"
                class="bg-maroon hover:bg-customBeige text-white font-bold py-2 px-6 sm:px-8 rounded-full uppercase text-sm sm:text-base"
            >
                SUPPORT NOW
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!--section step -->
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-1">
            <!-- Step 1 -->
            <div
                class="bg-maroon flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-6 pb-6 text-white rounded-lg shadow-lg"
            >
                <svg
                    class="-mt-4"
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                    width="60"
                    height="60"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    class="lucide lucide-pound-sterling mb-4"
                >
                    <path d="M18 7c0-5.333-8-5.333-8 0"></path>
                    <path d="M10 7v14"></path>
                    <path d="M6 21h12"></path>
                    <path d="M6 13h10"></path>
                </svg>
                <p class="text-lg font-semibold py-2 mt-3">Step 1</p>
                <p class="text-center font-semibold text-base">
                    We receive your donation of a water pump charity or water
                    well.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 2 -->
            <div
                class="bg-customBeige flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-6 text-dark rounded-lg shadow-lg"
            >
                <svg
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                    width="60"
                    height="60"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    class="lucide lucide-arrow-right-left mb-4"
                >
                    <path d="m16 3 4 4-4 4"></path>
                    <path d="M20 7H4"></path>
                    <path d="m8 21-4-4 4-4"></path>
                    <path d="M4 17h16"></path>
                </svg>
                <p class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Step 2</p>
                <p class="text-center font-semibold text-base">
                    We send it to your chosen country.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 3 -->
            <div
                class="bg-maroon flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-6 text-white rounded-lg shadow-lg"
            >
                <svg
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                    width="60"
                    height="60"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    class="lucide lucide-wrench mb-4"
                >
                    <path
                        d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"
                    ></path>
                </svg>
                <p class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Step 3</p>
                <p class="text-center font-semibold text-base">
                    It normally takes minimum 9 to 10 months to complete a Water
                    Hand Pump or Water Well.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 4 -->
            <div
                class="bg-customBeige flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-6 pb-6 text-dark rounded-lg shadow-lg"
            >
                <svg
                    class="duration-300 hover:stroke-maroon -mt-3"
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                    width="60"
                    height="60"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    class="lucide lucide-notepad-text mb-4"
                >
                    <path d="M8 2v4"></path>
                    <path d="M12 2v4"></path>
                    <path d="M16 2v4"></path>
                    <rect width="16" height="18" x="4" y="4" rx="2"></rect>
                    <path d="M8 10h6"></path>
                    <path d="M8 14h8"></path>
                    <path d="M8 18h5"></path>
                </svg>
                <p class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 mt-4">Step 4</p>
                <p class="text-center font-semibold text-base">
                    After the completion, you will receive a detailed report
                    with pictures, location & number of beneficiaries.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!--section 6-->
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <p class="text-grey font-bold text-3xl text-center py-4">
                See other Project
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <Otherproject SeeOtherProjects={otherproject} />
</Layout>
